{"petition_id":1252359,"title":"Davenport, IA City Council: Stop Fluoridating Our Water","status":"open","url":"http://api.change.org/petitions/davenport-ia-city-council-stop-fluoridating-our-water","overview":"<p>We have found:<br /><br />1) In Davenport, the type of fluoride cited in the 1952 Agreement - pharmaceutical-grade sodium fluoride - has been replaced with industrial-grade hydrofluorosilicic acid, a toxic substance contaminated with chemicals including arsenic and barium;<br />2) A World Health Organization (WHO) study shows no difference in cavity rates in fluoridated and non-fluoridated areas;<br />3) Ninety-seven percent of Western Europe has chosen fluoride-free water;<br />4) Fluoride is the only chemical added to drinking water for 'medication;'<br />5) Fluoridated water is no longer recommended for infants;<br />6) Ingestion of fluoride has been linked to thyroid problems, osteosarcoma (bone cancer), dental &amp; skeletal fluorosis, and reduced IQ;<br />7) Fluoridation poses added burden and risk to low-income communities;<br />8) Due to other sources, many people are being over-exposed to fluoride;<br />9) Dosage is not being controlled;<br />10) Fluoride is added to our drinking water without informed consent, i.e. the dangers of fluoridation are not addressed to the users of the Davenport Water System;<br /><br />It is our choice what we put into our bodies.<br /><br />Therefore, we the undersigned - residents, business owners, and people who visit and conduct business in the City of Davenport, IA - ask that the City Council introduces for a vote the issue of 'Elimination of Fluoride in the Davenport Municipal Drinking Water.'</p>","targets":[],"letter_body":"Stop fluoridating our water\r\n","signature_count":34,"image_url":"//d22r54gnmuhwmk.cloudfront.net/photos/7/zp/ot/XmzpotpFxBIVUNw-556x313-cropped.jpg","category":null,"goal":100,"created_at":"2013-08-06T03:22:20Z","end_at":"2014-08-06T23:59:59Z","creator_name":null,"creator_url":null,"organ